Package grafioschtrader.connector.instrument.twelvedata

Class TwelvedataFeedConnector

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.connector.instrument.BaseFeedConnector
grafioschtrader.connector.instrument.BaseFeedApiKeyConnector
grafioschtrader.connector.instrument.twelvedata.TwelvedataFeedConnector
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFeedConnector
@Component public class TwelvedataFeedConnector extends BaseFeedApiKeyConnector
Twelvedata's pricing model regulates both the number of accesses per minute and the availability of the functionality. A maximum number of accesses per minute or even per day is not implemented. The "Basic Free" price model also only provides US data. A regex check of the URL ending is not implemented. However, a check via the connector is available.
